sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 👤 User
    participant Browser as 🌐 Browser
    participant API as 🚀 Next.js API
    participant DB as 💾 db.json
    participant Resend as 📧 Resend

    User->>Browser: Enter email address
    Browser->>API: POST /api/auth/send-otp {email}
    API->>API: generateOtp() → 6-digit code
    API->>API: otpExpiresAt() → +10 min
    API->>DB: saveOtp(email, code, expiry)
    API->>Resend: sendOtpEmail(email, code)
    Resend-->>User: Email with 6-digit code
    API-->>Browser: {sent: true}
    Browser->>User: Show code input screen

    User->>Browser: Enter 6-digit code
    Browser->>API: POST /api/auth/verify-otp {email, code}
    API->>DB: verifyAndConsumeOtp(email, code)
    DB-->>API: valid ✓ (code deleted)
    API->>DB: upsertUser(email)
    API->>API: signToken(userId) → JWT
    API-->>Browser: Set httpOnly cookie + {email}
    Browser->>User: Logged in ✓
